# Open game after request

When you have **fully finished** handling the user's request (all edits done, no follow-up work left), open the Math rocket game in the default browser so they can try it.

Run this command once at the end of your response:

```bash
open "index.html"
```

Run it from the project root: `/Users/imor/Documents/Cursor Projects/Math rocket game/`. Prefer the full path if needed:

```bash
open "/Users/imor/Documents/Cursor Projects/Math rocket game/index.html"
```

Do not run it in the middle of a multi-step task—only after the request is complete.
